<parameter name="old_string">    category: 'research',
    helpText: 'Campus counseling centers can become overwhelmed with demand, especially during high-stress periods like finals or major life transitions, making external provider options essential for continuity of care. Research therapists, psychiatrists, and counseling centers in your college area who accept your insurance and specialize in young adult or college student mental health. Having established backup providers ensures you can access professional support even when campus services have long wait times or limited availability.'
  }
