    id: 'prompt-45',
    prompt: 'Research and complete the application process for mental health accommodations through your college\'s disability services office',
    category: 'action',
    helpText: 'Applying for mental health accommodations establishes formal documentation of your needs and creates official support systems before you encounter academic challenges. This process typically requires documentation from a mental health professional and can provide accommodations like extended test time, private testing rooms, or flexible attendance policies. Having approved accommodations in place gives you legal protections and immediate access to support when mental health symptoms impact your academic performance, removing barriers to success during difficult periods.'
  }
];</parameter>
<parameter name="new_string">  {
    id: 'prompt-45',
    prompt: 'Research and complete the application process for mental health accommodations through your college\'s disability services office',
    category: 'action',
    helpText: 'Applying for mental health accommodations establishes formal documentation of your needs and creates official support systems before you encounter academic challenges. This process typically requires documentation from a mental health professional and can provide accommodations like extended test time, private testing rooms, or flexible attendance policies. Having approved accommodations in place gives you legal protections and immediate access to support when mental health symptoms impact your academic performance, removing barriers to success during difficult periods.'
  },
  {
    id: 'prompt-46',
    prompt: 'Register for and actively participate in a campus physical fitness class or recreational activity to establish regular exercise as part of your mental health maintenance routine',
    category: 'action',
    helpText: 'Regular physical exercise is one of the most powerful tools for managing anxiety, depression, and stress during college, with benefits comparable to medication for many mental health conditions. Enrolling in a structured fitness class or joining a recreational sports team creates accountability and social connection while establishing this crucial mental health practice. Whether it\'s yoga, swimming, intramural sports, or group fitness classes, having scheduled physical activity helps regulate mood, improve sleep, and build resilience against college stressors.'
  }
];</parameter>
